OL,3,CSwiss bar uninspected for five years
OL,4,Cbefore deadly NYE fire, officials say
OL,6,FA bar that caught fire at the Swiss
OL,7,Fski resort of Crans-Montana, killing
OL,8,F40 people, had gone five years without
OL,9,Fa safety inspection, local officials
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe blaze broke out at the Le
OL,13,FConstellation bar during New Year's
OL,14,FEve celebrations, which also left 119
OL,15,Fpeople injured, and is believed to
OL,16,Fhave been caused by sparklers placed
OL,17,Finside champagne bottles.
