OL,6,FAt a press conference on Tuesday
OL,7,Fmorning, Crans-Montana's mayor,
OL,8,FNicolas Feraud, said the Le
OL,9,FConstellation bar had not been
OL,10,Finspected since 2020.
OL,12,FRegional authorities said safety
OL,13,Finspections were the responsibility of
OL,14,Fthe municipality.
OL,16,F"We regret this bitterly," Feraud
OL,17,Fsaid, adding that it will be up to
OL,18,Fjudicial authorities to determine
OL,19,Fwhat, if any, influence the lack of
OL,20,Finspections had on the events that led
OL,21,Fto the fire.
