OL,6,FHe said he could not immediately
OL,7,Fexplain why inspections had not been
OL,8,Fcarried out for so long.
OL,10,FIn September last year, an external
OL,11,Fexpert was asked to conduct a
OL,12,Fsoundproofing analysis and concluded
OL,13,Fthe bar complied with anti-noise
OL,14,Fregulations, Feraud added, without
OL,15,Ffurther comment.
OL,17,FFeraud also announced a ban on the use
OL,18,Fof the same type of sparklers in other
OL,19,Flocal venues.
