OL,6,FA preliminary investigation found that
OL,7,Fsparklers on bottles held too close to
OL,8,Fthe ceiling were the likely cause of
OL,9,Fthe fire.
OL,11,FAuthorities are now looking into
OL,12,Fwhether soundproofing material on the
OL,13,Fceiling conformed with regulations and
OL,14,Fwhether the candles were permitted for
OL,15,Fuse in the bar.
OL,17,FA criminal investigation has also been
OL,18,Fopened into the bar's managers.
